{"tid":307034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"台女控男DJ趁醉性侵 下體採樣DNA竟係...","createTime":"2017-07-03T04:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T11:50:51.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5ac3c59199b839ad1dfde6230d55d3e146c61dd","tid":307034,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"台灣台北市一名年約20多歲的女子，去年8月網上認識一名唐姓男唱片騎師（DJ），兩人相談甚歡，沒多久就約到夜店跳舞狂歡。酒酣耳熱之際，兩人搭的士到汽車旅館發生性關係，10天後女子卻報案，聲稱腦部動過手術有後遺症喝酒後會失憶，指控唐男趁她失憶時性侵她。<br />\n<br />\n台北地檢署調查後發現，女子體內驗到的男性DNA並非唐男，反而是其他男子，認為證據不足，決定不起訴唐男。<br />\n<br />\n女子指控，她以前酒量很好，但因曾動過腦部手術出現後遺症，只要喝了酒就會短暫失憶，而唐男就趁她喝醉後性侵她。她隔天醒來才獨自從旅館離開，她傳LINE給唐男，唐男都只讀不回，因此決定驗傷控告唐男涉嫌乘機性交罪。<br />\n<br />\n但唐男到案卻供稱，當天兩人喝酒後，自然而然的去汽車旅館開房，一開始都很正常，但期間女子突然抗拒，他就馬上停止，並沒有性侵女子。檢警指出，女子驗傷報告雖在其下體驗到男性的DNA，但和唐男的DNA比對後不符，女子下體的男性DNA其實另有其人。檢方認為，兩人進入旅館時並無異狀，且事後女子還不斷傳短訊探詢唐男近況，加上驗傷報告的DNA樣本和唐男並不符，認為證據不足，決定不起訴唐男。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/admin.thenet.ng/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Cristiano-Ronaldo-misses-penalty-against-Austria_Thenetng-GIF.gif?resize=561%2C317\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fadmin.thenet.ng%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2FCristiano-Ronaldo-misses-penalty-against-Austria_Thenetng-GIF.gif%3Fresize%3D561%252C317&h=0494f1bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ce4fe4ae813b033b40f8bdf1ccee5bbfae7499a","tid":307034,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"oh no"},{"pid":"b73194d08048ac0cb7e6d84b55461531c98d9fb0","tid":307034,"uid":69680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"台北市+1"},{"pid":"22ef26e8e6dba59ba482855b2232b859188d00a5","tid":307034,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c27224e1eeb681e503cd94153edd339a9e7c4a","tid":307034,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"又話有短暫失憶，又知係個男DJ做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b029331f9b5afed0cb089f0b15bed90cb7b6901f","tid":307034,"uid":37948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話有短暫失憶，又知係個男DJ做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n局部性短暫失憶"},{"pid":"b75640246414863400d7337a9406ecff7db9b52d","tid":307034,"uid":92095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"腦手術會有D咁既後遺症?係咪被害妄想之餘次次都飲到斷片咋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a782e0b46d9fa86702b1da50dd1e7f92a5a705","tid":307034,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"其實係咪勞資糾紛？"},{"pid":"92acd39b4377c07107ee5f950902ba53f7fd4fa7","tid":307034,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話有短暫失憶，又知係個男DJ做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n選擇性短暫失憶"},{"pid":"a10d947f6720747c60ca7912e3fc531ce61826fc","tid":307034,"uid":82317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"老強唔成立<br />\n有冇分加？"},{"pid":"ad936b6cbe61b21ad72e51471d2ea5a0d8f0f7f9","tid":307034,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"証明佢真係會失憶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ff503254ef4f2e2774567e67f2d2864eceb1c8","tid":307034,"uid":50862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"唔似勞資<br />\n似O趙完鬆"},{"pid":"8e01f45fc80258dcfe9b301feccab6dcaef2bdcf","tid":307034,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"大人英明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a4c17c1d652cc56c072